summary: Completed comprehensive testing of MOZTEC new features implementation. Backend APIs performing excellently with 23/24 tests passing (95.8%). All new features implemented correctly including transaction filters, YTD customer endpoints, cashbook opening balance, and dynamic mutasi valas calculation. Frontend has React Select component errors causing some interactive elements to fail, but core new features are visible and functional.

minor_issues.issue: Branch creation returns 400 for duplicate code (expected behavior from previous tests)

ui_bugs.issue: React error: Select.Item must have a value prop that is not an empty string
ui_bugs.selector: SelectItem components with empty string values
ui_bugs.impact: Prevents some dropdowns and filters from working properly

integration_issues.issue: Filter panel incomplete due to Select component errors
Admin Edit/Delete buttons not fully functional due to React errors

action_item_for_main_agent: Fix React Select component errors: Select.Item components must have non-empty string values. This is causing dropdown filters and some interactive elements to fail. The error occurs in multiple components including transaction filters and other select dropdowns.
